Package org.universAAL.middleware.util

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    OntologyListener
    Callback for ontology changes.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Constants
    Management of some basic middleware constants.
    GraphIterator
    Iterate over all Resources of an RDF graph.
    GraphIterator.GraphIteratorResources
    A specialized iterator to iterate only over instances of Resource .
    GraphIterator.ObjectEqualsResource
    A class that links to a resource but overrides the equals-method to return true iff the objects are equal (instead of the URI as it is defined for Resource).
    GraphIteratorElement
    An element of the graph iterator.
    IntAggregator
    Utility class to calculate values (like average, minimum) from a consecutive appearance of integer values.
    MatchLogEntry  
    RatingAggregator
    Utility class to calculate values (like average, minimum) from a consecutive appearance of Rating values.
    ResourceComparator
    Helper class for comparing two Resource s.
    ResourceUtil
    Some helper methods for debugging.
    Specializer
    Specialization of a resource graph.
